    <string name="question_5">5. In what year did Samsung launch the Galaxy S smartphone?</string>
    <string name="question_6">6. Which manufacturer was the first to introduce a 4K UHD display on a smartphone?</string>
    <string name="question_7">7. In what year did LG launch the G Flex smartphone?</string>
    <string name="question_8">8. What’s the biggest camera sensor ever to be fitted on a smartphone?</string>
    <string name="question_9">9. What’s the most fragile part of a smartphone?</string>
    <string name="question_10">10. Why is it so difficult and expensive to change the display of your smartphone?</string>
